{"type": "article", "id": 42417, "title": "拯救脱妆“尴尬癌”，我们发起了一场不脱妆挑战", "description": "远观还挺美，近看，啧啧啧，脱妆就是大写的尴尬", "date": "2017-06-27T15:27:34Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 10, "author": 18, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 124, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170627110850ifNJd6ponh9YCWue.jpg", "contents": "<h3>现实里总是充满着许多不可描述的尴尬。</h3><p>生活的神奇之处大概就在于你永远不知道下一秒会发生什么，当实际情况和我们所设想的不一样时，一些小情绪总会浮现出来，比如总有一些不可明说的羞愧难当让你的面部表情容易失控。</p><p>特别是对于内心戏比男人丰富千万倍的女人来说，更可能患上“尴尬症”。试想当你顶着没捋过的刘海，穿着花纹睡衣素颜就出门时，你可能会遇到前男友，前男友的现女友，现男友的前女友……尴尬得让你恨不得原地消失。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627110916YW2vLKjlmwZruUMC.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.557500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>出门在外，即使全副武装，也最怕空气突然的安静，最怕口红突然的脱妆。</p><p>当你以为周围所有人都忍不住多看你两眼，似乎是因为你的美貌时，千万别这么想。赶紧去洗手间，你就会发现，多半是口红粘牙了。OMG！此时的你除了尴尬到原地爆炸，别无出路。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627110941cBQiDKgfWCRAwljb.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.565553\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>当你换衣时看到领口的口红印，吃饭时小心翼翼却还是难逃脱妆，吸猫后发现脱得惨不忍睹的唇妆时，再好的心情也会down到谷底。</p><h3>为了拯救脱妆尴尬，我们发起了一场口红不脱妆挑战。</h3><p>你想象当中的罗曼蒂克桥段是，你用过的杯沿留下唇印，你风情万种眉眼妩媚地将高脚杯递给男朋友，男朋友再嘴角含笑地对准唇印喝一口……</p><p>Wake up！！！是时候从这么苏这么甜的梦里醒过来了。</p><p>在现实生活中往往是，你身边这位患有“直男癌”的男朋友，嫌弃地看看杯子，再看看你的嘴，“善意”地提醒：诶！你的口红要不要补一下……</p><p>毕竟你想象中的自己：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706271110048FlX2TnL5aHPfDRS.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">而现实中的你：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627111039w2tkP5BaglvA0GjR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.951562\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">想象总是太美好，现实却有不可描述的尴尬。扪心自问怎样才能拯救“尴尬癌”？最近，好奇心日报就联合兰蔻发起了一场口红不脱妆挑战，试试看用兰蔻摇摇染唇液，这款号称超级显色还能一整天持久不脱妆，喝什么都不留杯的神器是否能让真尴尬变零尴尬：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=b0517vh8cow&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>Round 1：试衣挑战</h3><p>试了那么多，但是想买的只有那一件。但想退的时候才发现，衣领沾上了口红印，面对售货员的嫌弃，尴尬值飙升，心情简直暴跌。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706271112020sVZrbcWiQFgfvJU.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">可是身边的闺蜜为什么已经选到了心仪的衣服，这会儿都在拍照晒朋友圈了呢？&nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627111216eYgj4u37iKskRdI8.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><b>想要试衣不尴尬，<a href=\"http://ad.doubleclick.net/ddm/trackclk/N8897.2103900QDAILY/B11526462.201221954;dc_trk_aid=401119397;dc_trk_cid=83153925\" rel=\"nofollow\">兰蔻摇摇染唇液</a>值满分！</b></p><h3>Round 2：美食挑战</h3><p>对于可爱的吃货姑娘来说，世界上最难的问题是美貌与美食如何兼得。一不小心放纵自己大快朵颐后，三明治和咖啡杯留下宠信过的痕迹并不算优雅的代名词。而吃什么都毫无压力的闺蜜永远比你少一步，快一秒，连一起合影你都被抓拍到在补妆的样子，简直尴尬爆炸。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627140730a7SPZripb9TGL1Vf.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627111401KjCStvNdeonMUTwG.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627111412b09TWsku5wLnMZfI.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><b>显色持久不脱妆，<a href=\"http://ad.doubleclick.net/ddm/trackclk/N8897.2103900QDAILY/B11526462.201221954;dc_trk_aid=401119397;dc_trk_cid=83153925\" rel=\"nofollow\">兰蔻摇摇染唇液</a>值满分！</b><br></p><h3>Round 3：吸猫挑战</h3><p>如果不巧，你还是一位善良的小仙女兼猫奴，那你多半还是吸猫重度患者。一日养猫，终生想猫，猫瘾一来，随手吸猫，根本顾不上嘴上的口红，其实这样会让你们家的小萌爪也很尴尬。快看，它被你亲的一身口红，满脸不情愿。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627111452RwxQpGHluENjvtdM.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627111439NJdaYXA5ps0IR1Wc.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><b>想要爱猫不留吻痕，<a href=\"http://ad.doubleclick.net/ddm/trackclk/N8897.2103900QDAILY/B11526462.201221954;dc_trk_aid=401119397;dc_trk_cid=83153925\" rel=\"nofollow\">兰蔻摇摇染唇液</a>值满分！</b><br></p><h3>值满分的摇摇染唇液，有这么多忠实的拥趸！</h3><p>兰蔻摇摇染唇液拥有能让外貌协会倾倒的调酒杯造型，黑色瓶盖带有品牌经典玫瑰印花实在美貌。海绵气垫式设计的刷头，超Q弹，上唇显色水润，秒变哑光质地，不见唇纹还显色，全新四色配方任意搭配：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706271116047gkxFacDpKYU1qG5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.892405\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627111622szyg1GavkTcBxm5f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.744304\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627111642lm4Yd1D9LENriHZR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.793671\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627111707qkQjMxSCHAnrRhET.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.769620\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">轻薄水润的兰蔻摇摇染唇液一上唇就会变干，完美地和唇部融为一体，完全没有其他唇釉的黏腻感觉，夏日最爱的哑光妆效，再也不用担心头发粘在嘴唇上了。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627111724BTFkKsDGyfr7PUeZ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">（试色来自于小五月maymay）</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">如果视频挑战中的三种场景还不够，那么再来看看兰蔻摇摇染唇液都拥有哪些忠实的拥趸。其实兰蔻摇摇染唇液不仅活跃于各大社交平台，是当之无愧的INS人气星品，它还获得了安迪的青睐，是女神刘涛的“好色”之选。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627111751YcZ8ekN1rBnDE46Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.315500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627111804hrfNVkuRomGsZOBC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666750\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><a href=\"http://ad.doubleclick.net/ddm/trackclk/N8897.2103900QDAILY/B11526462.201221954;dc_trk_aid=401119397;dc_trk_cid=83153925\" rel=\"nofollow\">（刘涛同款：#374）</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">除了刘涛，还有许多美妆达人们被它迷倒。可人儿的试色也非常值得一看和参考哦▼<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627111839o5SCGLpfdTyYqt9X.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">（试色来自于SI_u）</figcaption></figure></div><p><b>#270 Beige Vintage 甜甜粉豆沙</b></p><p>温柔的豆沙粉色让你气质与温柔并存。不挑肤色，成为爆款没毛病。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627111911QId1RX8HZV7OxDCJ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.690778\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">（试色来自于Luci_han）</figcaption></figure></div><p><b>#272 Peachy Nude 桃桃乌龙</b></p><p>略带橘调，要溢出屏幕的青春活泼的蜜桃色，元气少女就是你，少女感UP！UP！UP！</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627112014Au7NrR2QEzGeyopt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.003036\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">（试色来自于两碗芋圆）</figcaption></figure></div><p><b>#378 Pink Power 粉红火焰鸟</b></p><p>略带紫光的玫瑰粉色，绝对是不容错过的兰蔻经典色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706271120534sT9dFk1pr2YMEAm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">（试色来自于Anna_zhuxuan）</figcaption></figure></div><p><b>#374 Kiss Me Cherie 干杯车厘子</b></p><p>一抹浆果色的复古红，能让妹纸气场全开，那么干杯车厘子绝对不会让你失望。肤白貌美大长腿，前两项就全靠它了！</p><p>兰蔻摇摇染唇液不仅拯救你的尴尬癌，还让你的美貌无时不有，无处不在，无惧掉线。现在只要<b><a href=\"http://ad.doubleclick.net/ddm/trackclk/N8897.2103900QDAILY/B11526462.201221954;dc_trk_aid=401119397;dc_trk_cid=83153925\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里</a></b>就能获得这款约会必备神器，连Kiss都不会留下痕迹，四大IT色号任你选。用前记得摇一摇！<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627112159vjbRkXIWmfxCT8zG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.092405\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}